high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter between the sinks
Grab the spray bottle off of the counter
Turn left and go to the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting a spray bottle in the trash can

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the sinks.
Take the yellow spray bottle from between the sinks.
Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn right to face the toilet.
Put the bottle in the green bin to the left of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a spray bottle in a bin.

high_descs: Turn around and then move so that you're facing the bathroom sinks on the left.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle from behind the soap on the bathroom counter.
With the spray bottle in hand, move to face the trash can on the left of the toilet.
Throw the spray bottle away in the trash can.
